About

Hi, welcome to the main website for our project ‘A study of allelic series using transcriptomic phenotypes’. This website contains an HTML version of the iPython Notebook for our analysis. Here is the repository where all of the data is contained.

This website constitutes 100% of the Supplementary Material and Extended Results for our paper.

About the Authors
